<p>Opus is a borne out of the nationwide Circuit Breaker (CB) measures in response to the Covid-19 pandemic. Unfortunately, this seemingly innocuous period has revealed to many of us the sad reality of our productivity, and also our self-discipline in the grand scheme of things.</p>
<p>What was initially a dream come true for us soon morphed into a nightmare, as we found ourselves struggling to maintain productivity after having abruptly seized from us the familiar school routine that many of us has come to appreciate in this period.</p>

